<div class="level3">

<p>
The Linksys <span class="search_hit">NSLU2</span> has one button. See <a href="nslu2/nslu2.hardware.button" class="wikilink1" title="toh:linksys:nslu2:nslu2.hardware.button"><span class="search_hit">nslu2</span>.hardware.button</a> for some options with that.
- shut down via power button ( <a href="https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=25253" class="urlextern" title="https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=25253"  rel="nofollow">https://forum.openwrt.org/viewtopic.php?id=25253</a> )
</p>

</div>

